"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakawaAtN","text_ar":"رَكَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S,) Msb;) the latter allowable. (Msb.) The prov. (S)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaArati Alqawosu rakowapF","text_ar":"صَارَتِ القَوْسُ رَكْوَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bow became a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rkwp","text_ar":"ركوة"},{"kind":"text","text":", app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bow became exchanged for a vessel such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rkwp","text_ar":"ركوة"},{"kind":"text","text":", but see what follows,] is applied in relation to the retiring of good fortune, and reverse in the state of affairs. (S, K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A small"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaworaq","text_ar":"زَوْرَق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skiff"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (ISd, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruqoEap","text_ar":"رُقْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rag,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EawaASir","text_ar":"عَوَاصِر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three stones"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which grapes are pressed so as to force out the juice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placed one above another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the M. (TA.) [Hence, accord. to the TK, the prov. above mentioned: but I see not why.] ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faloham","text_ar":"فَلْهَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a woman; i. e. her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faroj","text_ar":"فَرْج"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vulva"},{"